MoodTransit (기분환승)

This software normally discovers public recommendation candidates through ListenBrainz and enriches them
with MusicBrainz-backed recording metadata. It does not claim that MusicBrainz, ListenBrainz, or any result
represents every recording or the complete catalog of a streaming provider.

